An Ambigous Geographical Area, But, for Now, Let's Call It a Delta
introduction: The last family from Delta Vacaresti will be evicted after the area will be declared a protected natural park. Tautu and his son-in-law collect the remaining metal from a nearby burned hut to make the next sell.
